song.title: Action Game BGM Demo
song.info:
"Action Game BGM" 2005 - Handheld & 2d Action - 10 channels - 8-bit 22khz samples
This catchy action tune was written as a demo for GBA/2D gaming, it could fit in games similar to metal slug or contra, and is originally a S3M module (199kb). This recording is in 44khz for your listening pleasure.
